    "type": "outdoor",
    "description": "# Waterdeep and the Sword Coast North\n\nThis map shows the City of Waterdeep and the surrounding region, including key locations relevant to the Shattered Crown adventure.\n\n## Key Locations\n- **Waterdeep** — The City of Splendors, built on and around Mount Waterdeep\n- **Undermountain** — Halaster Blackcloak's dungeon beneath the city (approach to Netherese ruins)\n- **Mount Waterdeep** — The mountain that the city is built around\n- **Sea of Swords** — The body of water to the west\n- **Chasm of the Maelstrom** — A dangerous underwater trench where one crown fragment lies\n- **Ancient Elven Ruins** — Drow territory to the south\n- **Ruins of Myth Drannor** — Ancient elven ruins far to the south\n- **Astral Plane Echo** — A mysterious rift in the sky above the city",
